query:
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `videoPerformanceCorrelation` (
  `id` int AUTO_INCREMENT NOT NULL,
  `userId` int NOT NULL,
  `videoId` int NOT NULL,
  `pirScoreBefore` int,
  `pirDimensionsBefore` json,
  `pirAssessmentIdBefore` int,
  `pirScoreAfter` int,
  `pirDimensionsAfter` json,
  `pirAssessmentIdAfter` int,
  `improvementScore` int,
  `dimensionsImproved` json,
  `videoWatchedAt` datetime NOT NULL,
  `pirBeforeDate` datetime,
  `pirAfterDate` datetime,
  `daysBetweenVideoAndAfterPIR` int,
  `createdAt` timestamp NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
  `updatedAt` timestamp NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP ON UPDATE CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
  CONSTRAINT `videoPerformanceCorrelation_id` PRIMARY KEY(`id`)
);
